<p>When I'm editing a post, one of the most common things that I end up doing* is fixing the capitalization of the names Apple's products, like in this question's title.</p>

<p><strong>How would people feel about automatically changing all instances of 'iname' or 'Iname' to 'iName'?
<br>I don't imagine that SE has this functionality built in, so consider this a feature request.</strong></p>

